A creditor in the Blockbuster Inc.
bankruptcy case sued Carl Icahn over claims the billionaire
improperly converted his equity stake to debt to take control of
the company after its reorganization.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Joel Rosenblatt in San Francisco at 
 jrosenblatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
